{
  "id": "69d7b11b9bf88c5a88e2454b",
  "title": "割り算九九",
  "created": 1775743268,
  "updated": 1775747971,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69d7b11b9bf88c5a88e2454b",
      "text": "割り算九九",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775743268,
      "updated": 1775743268
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7b1230000000000d24db3",
      "text": "[八算]と呼ばれる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775743268,
      "updated": 1775743287
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7b1360000000000d24db5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775743287,
      "updated": 1775743287
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7b1360000000000d24db6",
      "text": "[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/九九#八算 九九#八算]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775743287,
      "updated": 1775743316
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7b1480000000000d24db7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775743305,
      "updated": 1775743305
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7b1540000000000d24db8",
      "text": "商と余りを諳んじる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775743316,
      "updated": 1775743366
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7b1860000000000d24dbb",
      "text": "そろばんの珠を弾く動作と対応している。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775743366,
      "updated": 1775743366
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bf080000000000d24e1d",
      "text": "順序が、[[除数、被除数]]、商、余りであることに注意",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746825,
      "updated": 1775747233
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bf620000000000d24e1e",
      "text": "\t[$ 10a\\div b=q\\ {あまり}\\ r]の場合、[$ {\\color{#0e0}b,a},q,r]の順。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746914,
      "updated": 1775747207
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7c01f0000000000d24e1f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775747103,
      "updated": 1775747159
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7b1710000000000d24dba",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775743345,
      "updated": 1775743348
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc830000000000d24df9",
      "text": "10の倍数を1桁の数で割る",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746180,
      "updated": 1775746180
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc8a0000000000d24dfa",
      "text": "  割り切れる場合",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746187,
      "updated": 1775746244
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7b1540000000000d24db9",
      "text": "   二一天作五　（にいちてんさくのご）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775743316,
      "updated": 1775746244
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7c0f40000000000d24e21",
      "text": "  割り切れる場合（五の段）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775747317,
      "updated": 1775747357
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7b1ba0000000000d24dbc",
      "text": "   五一倍作二　（ごいちばいさくのに）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775743418,
      "updated": 1775746244
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bcec0000000000d24e01",
      "text": "  割り切れず、被除数の10の位と商が一致する（被除数の珠を動かさない）場合",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746285,
      "updated": 1775747459
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7b1c10000000000d24dbd",
      "text": "   六一下加四　（ろくいちかかし）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775743425,
      "updated": 1775746244
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bce80000000000d24e00",
      "text": "  割り切れず、被除数の10の位と商が一致しない（被除数の珠を動かす）場合",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746280,
      "updated": 1775747464
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7b1ea0000000000d24dbe",
      "text": "   三一三十一　（さんいちさんじゅういち）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775743466,
      "updated": 1775746282
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bcbc0000000000d24dff",
      "text": " 1桁の数を1桁の数で割る（割り切れるもののみ）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746237,
      "updated": 1775747508
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7b1240000000000d24db4",
      "text": "  二進一十　　（にっしんのいちじゅう）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775743269,
      "updated": 1775746241
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7b21c0000000000d24dc0",
      "text": "  四進二十　　（ししんのにじゅう）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775743516,
      "updated": 1775746241
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bb7a0000000000d24dcd",
      "text": "\t余りが出るタイプの割り算では余りを加えた桁に 10 以上たまることがある。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775745914,
      "updated": 1775747777
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7c2d40000000000d24e2b",
      "text": "\t\t五珠が 2 つあるそろばんを用いると、この際に覚えることが減る。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775747797,
      "updated": 1775747883
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7c29b0000000000d24e2a",
      "text": "\t\t同じことだが、五珠が 1 つあるそろばんを用いると、1桁に入り切らない分や加えるべき数を記憶せねばならない。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775747740,
      "updated": 1775747971
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7c0e70000000000d24e20",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775747304,
      "updated": 1775747304
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7beab0000000000d24e1a",
      "text": "除算九九図（東京師範学校）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746732,
      "updated": 1775746768
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bead0000000000d24e1b",
      "text": " https://dictionary.sanseido-publ.co.jp/column/mono06",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746734,
      "updated": 1775746738
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7beb10000000000d24e1c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746738,
      "updated": 1775746738
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bb5a0000000000d24dc5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775745883,
      "updated": 1775745883
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bde20000000000d24e14",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746531,
      "updated": 1775746673
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7c1d10000000000d24e22",
      "text": "\t二の段",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775747538,
      "updated": 1775747550
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bb710000000000d24dc7",
      "text": "  二一天作五\tにいちてんさくのご",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775745905,
      "updated": 1775747552
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24dce",
      "text": "  二進一十　\tにしんのいちじゅう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747552
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24dcf",
      "text": " 三の段",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747557
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7c1e00000000000d24e23",
      "text": "  三一三十一\tさんいちさんじゅうのいち",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775747553,
      "updated": 1775747559
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24dd0",
      "text": "  三二六十二\tさにろくじゅうのに",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747559
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24dd1",
      "text": "  三進一十　\tさんしんのいちじゅう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747559
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24dd2",
      "text": " 四の段",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747569
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7c1e80000000000d24e24",
      "text": "  四一二十二\tしいちにじゅうのに",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775747560,
      "updated": 1775747571
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24dd3",
      "text": "  四二天作五\tしにてんさくのご",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747571
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24dd4",
      "text": "  四三七十二\tしさんしちじゅうのに",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747571
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24dd5",
      "text": "  四進一十　\tししんのいちじゅう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747571
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7c1f40000000000d24e25",
      "text": "\t五の段",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775747572,
      "updated": 1775747575
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7be050000000000d24e15",
      "text": "  五一倍作二　ごいちばいさくのに",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746565,
      "updated": 1775747578
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7be050000000000d24e16",
      "text": "  五二倍作四　ごにばいさくのし",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746566,
      "updated": 1775747578
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7be060000000000d24e17",
      "text": "  五三倍作六　ごさんばいさくのろく",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746567,
      "updated": 1775747578
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7be070000000000d24e18",
      "text": "  五四倍作八　ごしばいさくのはち",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746567,
      "updated": 1775747578
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7be070000000000d24e19",
      "text": "  五進一十　　ごしんのいちじゅう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746567,
      "updated": 1775747579
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bdca0000000000d24e02",
      "text": " 六の段",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746507,
      "updated": 1775747584
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7c1fd0000000000d24e26",
      "text": "  六一加下四\tろくいちかかし",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775747582,
      "updated": 1775747587
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24ddc",
      "text": "  六二三十二\tろくにかかに",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747587
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24ddd",
      "text": "  六三天作五\tろくさんてんさくのご",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747587
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24dde",
      "text": "  六四六十四\tろくしろくじゅうのし",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747587
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24ddf",
      "text": "  六五八十二\tろくごはちじゅうのに",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747587
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24de0",
      "text": "  六進一十　\tろくしんのいちじゅう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747587
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24de1",
      "text": " 七の段",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747593
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7c2040000000000d24e27",
      "text": "  七一加下三\tしちいちかかさん",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775747589,
      "updated": 1775747596
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24de2",
      "text": "  七二加下六\tしちにかかろく",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747596
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24de3",
      "text": "  七三四十二\tしちさんしじゅうのに",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747596
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24de4",
      "text": "  七四五十五\tしちしごじゅうのご",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747596
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24de5",
      "text": "  七五七十一\tしちごしちじゅうのいち",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747596
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24de6",
      "text": "  七六八十四\tしちろくはちじゅうのし",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747596
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24de7",
      "text": "  七進一十　\tしちしんのいちじゅう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747596
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24de8",
      "text": " 八の段",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747600
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7c20d0000000000d24e28",
      "text": "  八一加下二\tはちいちかかに",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775747597,
      "updated": 1775747603
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24de9",
      "text": "  八二加下四\tはちにかかし",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747603
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24dea",
      "text": "  八三加下六\tはちさんかかろく",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747603
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24deb",
      "text": "  八四天作五\tはちしてんさくのご",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747603
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24dec",
      "text": "  八五六十二\tはちごろくじゅうのに",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747603
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24ded",
      "text": "  八六七十四\tはちろくしちじゅうのし",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747603
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24dee",
      "text": "  八七八十六\tはちしちはちじゅうのろく",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747603
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24def",
      "text": "  八進一十　\tはっしんのいちじゅう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747603
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24df0",
      "text": " 九の段",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747615
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7c2140000000000d24e29",
      "text": "  九一加下一\tくいちかかいち",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775747604,
      "updated": 1775747618
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24df1",
      "text": "  九二加下二\tくにかかに",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747618
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24df2",
      "text": "  九三加下三\tくさんかかさん",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747618
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24df3",
      "text": "  九四加下四\tくしかかし",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747618
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24df4",
      "text": "  九五加下五\tくごかかご",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747618
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24df5",
      "text": "  九六加下六\tくろくかかろく",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747618
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24df6",
      "text": "  九七加下七\tくしちかかしち",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747618
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24df7",
      "text": "  九八加下八\tくはちかかはち",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
      "updated": 1775747618
    },
    {
      "id": "69d7bc600000000000d24df8",
      "text": "  九進一十　\tきゅうしんのいちじゅう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775746144,
